In the pupsp3 source directory

To build debuggable binaries and libraries type : buildP3.csh tty cluster force default debug
To build optimised binaries and libraries type  : buildP3.csh tty cluster force default

This will install PUPSP3 binaries in

~/bin

The PUPSP3 libraries will be installed in:

~/lib

and "man" pages in:

~/man

Header and support files will be installed in:

~/p3

To link PUPS/P3 library functions add -lpups to your linker directives
in makefile - you can use the P3 configure tool against an appropriate
Make.in file, there are examples (e.g. Make_fsw.in) in the pupscore.src
subdirectory within the pupsp3 source directory

